Package: simfast
Type: Package
Title: Isotonic Single-Index Regression Models with Generalized Link Functions
Version: 0.1.1
Description: Fitting isotonic single-index generalized regression models 
    via maximum likelihood and exact methods with formula support and 
    multiple distribution family and link function support.
